article_id:1874,category_name:News,title_name:A New Summon Showcase, Cursed Connections (Part One), Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>A summon showcase, Cursed Connections (Part One), went live at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1609394400"></span>! This summon showcase includes a limited-time adventurer and dragon. Featured adventurers and dragons also have a boosted appearance rate!</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);"><strong>The newly added 5★ adventurer Seimei and 5★ dragon Gozu Tenno will also appear in the upcoming Cursed Connections (Part Two) summon showcase starting at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1609999200"></span>, but of the two only Gozu Tenno will be featured in that showcase.</strong></span></div><div><br></div><div>Newly added limited-time featured adventurer and dragon:</div><div>■Adventurer</div><div>5★ Seimei (flame/wand)</div><div><br></div><div>■Dragon</div><div>5★ Gozu Tenno (flame)</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);"><strong>In this summon showcase, the following limited-time adventurers and dragons make their return. These adventurers and dragons are not featured in this showcase. They will also appear in the upcoming Cursed Connections (Part Two) summon showcase, but they will not be featured in that showcase either.</strong></span></div><div><br></div><div>Returning limited-time adventurers and dragons:</div><div>■Adventurers</div><div>5★ Mitsuhide (light/dagger)</div><div>5★ Nobunaga (flame/blade)</div><div>5★ Ieyasu (shadow/blade)</div><div>4★ Chitose (light/wand)</div><div>4★ Sazanka (shadow/axe)</div><div>4★ Addis (wind/blade)</div><div><br></div><div>■Dragons</div><div>5★ Daikokuten (light)</div><div>5★ Marishiten (shadow)</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);"><strong>Wyrmsigils may only be redeemed in the summon showcase from which they were earned. Wyrmsigils earned from the Cursed Connections (Part One) showcase cannot be redeemed in the Cursed Connections (Part Two) showcase. The 5★ adventurer Seimei will not be eligible for redemption using wyrmsigils from the Cursed Connections (Part Two) showcase.</strong></span></div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for showcase summons:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1609394400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1609999199"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the featured adventurer and dragon below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurer:</div><div>
